# Task 2: Sentiment Analysis

This repository contains Task 2 of the CodTech Machine Learning Internship.

## Objective
To perform sentiment analysis using TF-IDF and Logistic Regression.

## Files
- sentiment_analysis.ipynb
- sentiment_data.csv
- task2_report.docx
- output_screenshot.png

## Result
Model trained and evaluated with accuracy of ~90%.
